title: Index of Wholesale Trade Sales of Groceries for Federal Reserve District 5: Richmond
notes:
Indexes Were Computed By NBER From Percentage Changes Between Corresponding Months Of Successive Years. Source: Computed By NBER From Figures Supplied By The Federal Reserve Bank Of Richmond (For 1923-1937) And The U.S. Department Of Commerce (1938-1940); Data For 1938-1940 Are Published In Monthly Review Of The Federal Reserve Bank
